author: ALI TADAYON
title: JURUPA VALLEY: Man shot to death found in roadway
text:
BY ALI TADAYON / STAFF WRITER
Published: Oct. 10, 2015 Updated: 10:26 a.m. JURUPA VALLEY: Man shot to death found in roadway Print Photo Share Pin It More Galleries ADVERTISEMENT Related article » A man was shot to death Friday, Oct. 9, in the� 5300 block of Odell Street in Jurupa Valley, Riverside County sheriff's officials said.
Sheriff's officials did not disclose the man's name, age and hometown pending notificiation of next of kin.
Deputies were dispatched to the scene about 11:10 p.m. after receiving reports of a shooting in the area, according to a Sheriff's Department news release. Upon arrival, they found a man in the roadway suffering from gunshot wounds.
Deputies who first arrived on scene administered first aid to the victim before he was transported to a hospital. He later died.
The Sheriff's Department asks that anyone with information regarding the shooting contact Central Homicide Unit investigators at 951-955-2777 or Jurupa Valley Sheriff's Station investigators at 951-955-2600.
